---
/**
 * 404 body component.
 *
 * Privacy contract (PRD / UI_GUIDE):
 *   - Wording must NOT disclose whether a note ever lived at this path.
 *   - Forbidden vocabulary: "비공개", "삭제됨", "private", "deleted".
 *     The replacement phrasing is intentionally ambiguous — covers both
 *     "never existed" and "previously public, now unpublished".
 *   - The component reads NO props. The slug / request path / referrer are
 *     all considered information; echoing any of them back to the user can
 *     confirm a guess about a private note's existence.
 *
 * v0.2 visual: side-margin "404" numeral on `lg+` (8rem column), stacked
 * above title on mobile. Layout / type rules live in `components.css`.
 */
---
<section class="not-found">
  <div class="not-found__numeral" aria-hidden="true">404</div>
  <div>
    <h1 class="not-found__title">페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다</h1>
    <p class="not-found__body">요청하신 페이지가 존재하지 않거나, 더 이상 공개되지 않습니다.</p>
    <p class="not-found__home"><a href="/">→ home</a></p>
  </div>
</section>
